      <title>特朗普上台后，媒体高管交易增多，监管减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/executives-see-more-media-deals-less-regulation-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着共和党人唐纳德·特朗普当选美国总统，媒体高管们看到了更多合并和放松管制的可能性，这将促进广播和电视帝国的扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/executives-see-more-media-deals-less-regulation-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:12:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
