    <item>
      <title>Lyft 首席执行官希望联邦对自动驾驶汽车进行监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/lyft-ceo-wants-federal-autonomous-car-regulation-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lyft 首席执行官 David Risher 讨论了应对唐纳德·特朗普第二任总统的计划。他希望看到联邦法规明确共享乘车司机的就业状况和自动驾驶汽车的监管。他接受了彭博科技主持人 Ed Ludlow 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/lyft-ceo-wants-federal-autonomous-car-regulation-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 17:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>康普未能达成债务协议，盘前股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/commscope-fails-to-reach-debt-deal-shares-tumble-in-premarket</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康普控股公司 (CommScope Holding Co.) 的债券和股票周四下跌，此前该公司发布了第三季度业绩并表示尚未与一组债权人达成债务再融资或资本重组协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/commscope-fails-to-reach-debt-deal-shares-tumble-in-premarket</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:30:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华纳兄弟借助海外扩张赢得流媒体订阅用户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/warner-bros-boosts-streaming-subscribers-on-international-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[流媒体服务 Max 的母公司华纳兄弟探索公司第三季度新增订阅用户数超出预期，表明其在线业务正在回暖。该公司股价创下两年多以来的最大盘中涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/warner-bros-boosts-streaming-subscribers-on-international-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:26:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国监管机构对 Polymarket 进行调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/crypto-bets-on-trump-polymarket-examined-by-french-regulator-anj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统大选期间用户需求激增后，法国博彩监管机构正在审查基于加密货币的预测市场平台 Polymarket 的运营情况，以查看其是否遵守规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/crypto-bets-on-trump-polymarket-examined-by-french-regulator-anj</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:11:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高通和 Arm 股价上涨，因盈利预示智能手机市场将反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/qualcomm-arm-results-show-phone-industry-making-uneven-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家严重依赖智能手机市场的芯片公司高通公司 (Qualcomm Inc.) 和 Arm Holdings Plc 的股价周四上涨，此前这两家公司发布的财报显示，需求将暂时回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/qualcomm-arm-results-show-phone-industry-making-uneven-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:34:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 因国家安全被勒令关闭加拿大部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/tiktok-ordered-to-close-canada-unit-on-national-security-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大下令字节跳动有限公司关闭其在该国的子公司，但此举不会阻止加拿大人使用这款由中国支持的流行社交视频应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/tiktok-ordered-to-close-canada-unit-on-national-security-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 22:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Match 下调全年业绩预期，扭转颓势势头受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/match-issues-soft-revenue-forecast-amid-activist-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Match Group Inc. 下调了全年营收预期，这令那些原本预计这家约会应用公司将在激进投资者的压力下扭亏为盈的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/match-issues-soft-revenue-forecast-amid-activist-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 21:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>创纪录的出行量推动 Lyft 盈利前景强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/lyft-raises-earnings-outlook-as-monthly-plan-draws-commuters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lyft Inc. 发布了本季度和全年强劲的盈利预期，此后该公司股价飙升，表明该叫车服务吸引更多通勤者的计划正在奏效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/lyft-raises-earnings-outlook-as-monthly-plan-draws-commuters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 21:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
